article.description: — Ricardo Wright had 29 points as Marist narrowly defeated VMI 78-74 in overtime on Saturday.
article.headline: Wright scores 29 to lift Marist over VMI 78-74 in OT
article.linkText: Wright scores 29 to lift Marist over VMI 78-74 in OT
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. -- — Ricardo Wright had 29 points as Marist narrowly defeated VMI 78-74 in overtime on Saturday. Noah Harris had 12 points for Marist (2-2). Samkelo Cele added 11 points and eight rebounds. Raheim Sullivan had 11 points. Kamdyn Curfman scored 27 points for the Keydets (2-2). Sean Conway added 18 points and eight rebounds. Jake Stephens had 13 points, six assists and four blocks. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
